        "\n",
        "\n",
        "### Implementation\n",
        "\n",
        "The comparator is realised in the following way\n",
        "\n",
        "![StrongArm Circuit](figures/comp/comp_test.svg){#fig-xschem_comp}\n",
        "\n",
